---
title: Autumn Squash and Pesto Flatbread with Red Onions and Parmesan Cheese
description: Enjoy this season’s best produce on a tomato-topped flatbread. Between sweet butternut squash, creamy pesto and crunchy pepitas, this dinner will leave you dreaming about opening a pizzeria.
